Description: sum of ntra, ntri and amon
Ecological quality ratio on a scale from 0-1 where 0.2, 0.4, 0.6 and 0.8 represent status boundaries bad-poor, poor-moderate, moderate-good and good-high.
Indicator specific EQR scales and boundaries also indicator specific, see HVMFS 2013-19 and tables in resources/utilities.
Quality factor specific EQR scales and boundaries also quality factor specific, see HVMFS 2013-19 and tables in resources/utilities.
